snippet.textDisplay:
Tum bhi humi ho
Hum bhi tumhi hain.

Such beautifully simply and heart touching lines! I love everything about this song. Such a serene and calming yet visually and vocally melodic song! The lyrics are soothing and empowering. I am so happy to see Zeb Bangash back on Coke Studio. This is a spellbinding symphony from Nizam, Noorima, Zeb and musicians that looks, sounds and feels like a fairytale. The message of interconnectivity of all life forms is beautifully portrayed. Love it!!
